Process visualization Statistical models

Model 0: comparing logistic with linear for task 3-6

Model 0 compares a multilevel logistic regression (a) for tasks 3-6 (that have a binary outcome) against a linear model. The two models are compared side by side and we see similar significant effects in both models for the same factors. An estimated means plot is provided for both models. As the models are comparable we are able to run one (linear model across all 6 tasks in the next section.
